WEBVTT

00:00.153 --> 00:01.014
Hi friends!

00:01.093 --> 00:01.651
How are you?

00:02.741 --> 00:04.729
Today we are going to learn the days of the week.

00:05.769 --> 00:06.371
Monday.

00:08.075 --> 00:08.755
Tuesday.

00:09.220 --> 00:09.905
Wednesday.

00:11.201 --> 00:11.811
Thursday.

00:13.021 --> 00:13.560
Friday.

00:15.093 --> 00:16.384
Saturday and Sunday.

00:17.555 --> 00:19.126
And then, the week starts again.

00:19.763 --> 00:24.172
Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday, Friday, Saturday and Sunday.

00:24.389 --> 00:25.238
And the months.

00:26.761 --> 00:28.847
January, it's cold.

00:29.881 --> 00:31.491
February, carnival!

00:32.132 --> 00:34.249
March, welcome spring.

00:35.539 --> 00:36.925
April showers bring...

00:37.748 --> 00:38.747
...May flowers.

00:39.753 --> 00:41.654
June, the sun shines.

00:42.691 --> 00:44.396
July, let's go to the beach.

00:45.414 --> 00:47.060
August, it's so hot.

00:48.063 --> 00:49.963
September, back to school.

00:50.860 --> 00:53.751
October, the leaves on the trees fall.

00:54.594 --> 00:56.773
November starts with Halloween.

00:57.642 --> 00:59.612
December, Christmas holidays.

